body.description: LASTS ALL YEAR. GUARANTEED!* Designed for customization, this Five Star Interactive Composition Book starts with table of contents pages where students can list topics, date and page number. This 1 subject composition book has 100 double-sided, college ruled sheets that feature a side margin and page number block for easy labeling. An inside pocket provides added storage. Customize your notebook! Slide your favorite photos into the clearview cover or create subject labels. A grid ruled reference guide is perfect for frequently referenced information such as periodic tables, multiplication tables or glossary of terms. Reference guide and table of contents are made with thick cardstock to stand up to regular use. The water-resistant, durable plastic cover helps protect notes. The large 9" x 11" pages do not have binder holes or perforation, providing plenty of room to glue inserts and cut-outs. 3 pack available in Forest Green, Fire Red and Pacific Blue. *Guarantee is valid for one year from purchase date. Does not cover misuse.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: MADE TO LAST Count on Five Star throughout the year. Our non-perforated high-quality paper and water-resistant cover helps keep notes neat and protected. Plus, we made our table of contents and reference pages with thicker paper to help them stand up to daily use. DESIGNED WITH TEACHERS Interactive notetaking is a hands-on approach to help students organize and retain information. Five Star teamed up with teachers to design this notebook which, contains a table of contents, reference guides, side margins and page number blocks for simplified organization. KEEP IT ALL TOGETHER From the classroom, to home and everywhere in between, we’re here to help students stay on top of every project. A large inside pocket stores full size sheets, while 2 smaller pockets have secure flap closures and are perfect for cut-outs and supplies.

reviews.reviewText: Wanted something to use in the classroom. I searched for these and ordered them. I love how sturdy these are. Great to use for interactive notebooks. Will order more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 28, 2021
reviews.reviewText: The paper feels thicker. The cover is durable. The space in the margins and for the page number is really nice. You write the title on the side instead of the top so as you are flipping through, you can see the titles of the pages. It’s well designed. Very good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I really like these notebooks
reviews.reviewText: These note books are well made. I like the cover with the insert so I could personalize it with artwork and title. It has a pocket on the inside for paper storage. I expect the pages to withstand repetitive use through time. The table of content pages are made of sturdy paper. My only wish is a label insert on the side so I can reach for the one I want at a glance when they are stacked.
